Description: major mode for git commit history ala gitk
 An interface to git commands which are not part of git.el. Primarily, this
 is a view of the git commit history with the ability to mark ranges and/or
 single commits and operate on them. Mutiple branches/tags/ref interfaces
 can be active at the same time.
 .
 Basic use:
 .
    M-x egit       View history of branch, tag, or other ref
    M-x egit-file  View commits related to a specific file
    M-x egit-dir   View commits related to files within a directory
